data.description:
3 bed/3.5 bath townhome. Solar to help with electric bill on those hot Florida summers. Property features a spacious floor plan with tile and laminate floors throughout. There are three bedrooms, each with their own bathroom, and an additional half bath downstairs. This corner unit has two patios on the main level (one off the main living area, the other off the downstairs master) and a balcony on the upper level. Washer and dryer included (but not warranted).Additional parking available. Pets upon approval. Community pool just steps away or walk down to the private bay access for fishing or just enjoying the view. Just minutes away from the Gulf's most beautiful beaches, shopping, restaurants, and more.

1 year lease. Credit and background check. Pets upon approval
